srael-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-may-have-the-worlds-most-moral-army-but-not-the-most-moral-leadership/0000018f-e3f2-d6db-a7bf-efff60d10000</guid></item><item><title>Radiohead 吉他手顶住了 BDS 与以色列艺术家合作的压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/radiohead-guitarist-pushes-back-against-bds-pressure-for-collaboration-with-israeli-artist/0000018f-e81b-d6de-a7df-fe3b70a60000</link><description>英国吉他手兼摇滚乐队 Radiohead 成员乔尼·格林伍德 (Jonny Greenwood) 正在与老朋友兼合作者、以色列著名音乐家杜杜·塔萨 (Dudu Tassa) 一起在欧洲巡演。面对 BDS 取消巡演的压力，格林伍德称批评者“不进步”</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/radiohead-guitarist-pushes-back-against-bds-pressure-for-collaboration-with-israeli-artist/0000018f-e81b-d6de-a7df-fe3b70a60000</guid></item><item><title>女人质？加沙战争？这位以色列极右翼议员担心的是其他事情：未婚女性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hostages-gaza-war-this-israeli-mk-is-worried-about-something-else-unmarried-women/0000018f-e81c-d1da-adaf-fd9fd3f40000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特议员利莫尔·桑·哈尔·梅莱赫在以色列议会核心小组会议上哀叹的不是被关押在加沙的以色列人质的命运，而是极端正统派妇女面临的最严重问题：找不到丈夫</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 12:06:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hostages-gaza-war-this-israeli-mk-is-worried-about-something-else-unmarried-women/0000018f-e81c-d1da-adaf-fd9fd3f40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列表示将把斯德·泰曼拘留中心转变为短期拘留设施，以减少巴勒斯坦囚犯的数量</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-sde-teiman-into-short-term-holding-facility-with-fewer-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-e7f4-d11f-a5cf-e7ff66cc0000</link><description>在向以色列最高法院提交有关斯德泰曼设施拘留条件的请愿书后，法官要求该州提供有关囚犯条件的答案。该州告知法院，他们正在转移囚犯并改善条件</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 11:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-turns-sde-teiman-into-short-term-holding-facility-with-fewer-palestinian-prisoners/0000018f-e7f4-d11f-a5cf-e7ff66cc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列秘密针对美国立法者发起加沙战争影响力活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-secretly-targeted-american-lawmakers-with-gaza-war-influence-campaign/0000018f-e7c8-d11f-a5cf-e7cb62af0000</link><description>为了影响全球公众对加沙战争的看法，虚假账户和网站传播亲以色列和仇视伊斯兰教的内容。该行动由以色列侨民事务部精心策划，并由一家政治竞选公司运营</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-secretly-targeted-american-lawmakers-with-gaza-war-influence-campaign/0000018f-e7c8-d11f-a5cf-e7cb62af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人希望人质归还。那么为什么内塔尼亚胡政府忽视他们呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israelis-want-the-hostages-back-so-why-is-netanyahus-government-ignoring-them/0000018f-e3fd-d821-a7df-f3fd29520000</link><description>在一次又一次的民意调查中，大多数以色列人将归还加沙哈马斯扣押的人质视为国家优先事项。但内塔尼亚胡政府不需要调查就知道这是道义上的当务之急</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 10:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israelis-want-the-hostages-back-so-why-is-netanyahus-government-ignoring-them/0000018f-e3fd-d821-a7df-f3fd29520000</guid></item><item><title>男子砸碎特拉维夫国土报办公室正门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/man-smashes-main-entrance-of-haaretz-offices-in-tel-aviv/0000018f-e7bb-d6de-a7df-f7bb0cc60000</link><description>身份不明的袭击者砸碎大门后逃离现场。国土报已通知以色列警方</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/man-smashes-main-entrance-of-haaretz-offices-in-tel-aviv/0000018f-e7bb-d6de-a7df-f7bb0cc60000</guid></item><item><title>拜登发表讲话后，加沙人民寄予厚望，但他们知道球在以色列手中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-in-gaza-for-cease-fire-but-they-know-that-the-ball-is-in-israels-court/0000018f-e76b-d6de-a7df-f76b47050000</link><description>加沙的几名巴勒斯坦人接受《国土报》采访，表达了对哈马斯和以色列之间停火谈判近期进展的谨慎乐观态度。加沙中部的一位母亲表示，加沙人“精疲力竭”，并“害怕谈判失败”</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:14:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-in-gaza-for-cease-fire-but-they-know-that-the-ball-is-in-israels-court/0000018f-e76b-d6de-a7df-f76b47050000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派的支持使人质交易更有可能，但内塔尼亚胡仍未做出决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-support-makes-hostage-deal-more-likely-but-netanyahu-is-still-undecided/0000018f-e739-db2a-a5ff-e73becc90000</link><description>在正统党派沙斯党和团结正义联盟明确支持拜登停火提议后，内塔尼亚胡对极右翼伙伴的反对有了一定的保障，但随着以色列北部的燃烧和焦点转移到黎巴嫩，人质问题可能会再次从中心淡出阶段</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 08:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-support-makes-hostage-deal-more-likely-but-netanyahu-is-still-undecided/0000018f-e739-db2a-a5ff-e73becc90000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷日：《国土报》记者在旧城横冲直撞时遭到右翼犹太青年袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-beefs-up-security-ahead-of-jerusalem-day-celebrations-with-a-history-of-violence/0000018f-e4c3-d908-a9cf-ede320aa0000</link><description>预计将有数万人参加一年一度的升旗游行，游行将穿过大马士革门和老城穆斯林区的街道</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-beefs-up-security-ahead-of-jerusalem-day-celebrations-with-a-history-of-violence/0000018f-e4c3-d908-a9cf-ede320aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在黎巴嫩边境陷入战略陷阱——得益于内塔尼亚胡的焦土政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-in-a-strategic-trap-on-lebanon-border-thanks-to-netanyahus-scorched-earth-policy/0000018f-e4f1-d908-a9cf-edf3f5ff0000</link><description>以色列政府不仅没有解决北部边境肆虐的冲突的办法，而且迄今为止的失败可能意味着许多以色列人决定永远不再返回那里的家园。 而本-格维尔，比消防员更纵火狂，总是手边煽风点火</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-in-a-strategic-trap-on-lebanon-border-thanks-to-netanyahus-scorched-earth-policy/0000018f-e4f1-d908-a9cf-edf3f5ff0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨从政府辞职将取决于人质谈判的进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-resignation-from-the-government-will-depend-on-progress-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018f-e4c5-d908-a9cf-ede7517e0000</link><description>本尼·甘茨 (Benny Gantz) 宣布，如果他的要求在 6 月 8 日之前得不到满足，他将辞去政府职务，但由于拜登总统宣布可能达成人质交易，他的离职现在受到质疑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 03:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-resignation-from-the-government-will-depend-on-progress-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018f-e4c5-d908-a9cf-ede7517e0000</guid></item><item><title>火灾后访问北部，内塔尼亚胡表示以色列准备对黎巴嫩采取“强有力的行动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-live/u-s-says-response-from-hamas-on-ceasefire-proposal-still-awaited-cia-chief-to-visit-doha/0000018f-e630-d2b4-a5cf-fffd966e0000</link><description>以色列秘密针对美国立法者开展加沙战争影响力活动 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：袭击者向美国大使馆开枪，被黎巴嫩军队士兵逮捕 ■ 美国表示正在等待哈马斯对停火提议的回应 ■ 以色列内阁授权以色列国防军增加数量到 8 月底，预备役军人人数将达到 35 万人 ■ 枪手向美国驻黎巴嫩大使馆开枪</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article-live/u-s-says-response-from-hamas-on-ceasefire-proposal-still-awaited-cia-chief-to-visit-doha/0000018f-e630-d2b4-a5cf-fffd966e0000</guid></item><item><title>对于来自以色列基布兹的难民来说，人质的死亡再次唤醒了 10 月 7 日的创伤和愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/for-refugees-from-this-kibbutz-hostages-deaths-reawakens-the-trauma-and-anger-of-oct-7/0000018f-e4f5-d908-a9cf-edf79b810000</link><description>本周，饱受摧残的加沙边境基布兹尼尔奥兹社区遭受了自哈马斯近八个月前残暴袭击以来最严重的打击：官方确认其在加沙的人质已经死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/for-refugees-from-this-kibbutz-hostages-deaths-reawakens-the-trauma-and-anger-of-oct-7/0000018f-e4f5-d908-a9cf-edf79b810000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 任命埃利奥特·勃兰特 (Elliot Brandt) 为下一任首席执行官，接替长期担任首席执行官的霍华德·科尔 (Howard Kohr)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/aipac-names-elliot-brandt-as-next-ceo-replacing-longtime-chief-howard-kohr/0000018f-e537-dce5-abdf-e73fec820000</link><description>勃兰特是这个强大的亲以色列组织的现任副首席执行官，他上任之际，AIPAC 正在瞄准被认为批评以色列的进步民主党人，并加强其对共和党初选的参与。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:55:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-05/ty-article/.premium/aipac-names-elliot-brandt-as-next-ceo-replacing-longtime-chief-howard-kohr/0000018f-e537-dce5-abdf-e73fec820000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院在拜登反对下通过国际刑事法院制裁法案，亲以色列民主党加入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</link><description>该法案是对国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗向总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-icc-sanctions-bill-amid-biden-opposition-with-pro-israel-dems-joining/0000018f-e4f9-db2a-a5ff-e4fbf3720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队希望加剧黎巴嫩战斗，担心公众不知道后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</link><description>以色列国防军负责人表示，以色列已准备好向黎巴嫩发动攻势，旨在让公众为更广泛的冲突做好准备。战时内阁周二晚上召开会议，与真主党讨论升级问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-wants-to-intensify-lebanon-fighting-fears-public-unaware-of-consequences/0000018f-e4d0-d1da-adaf-f5dfa6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>斯洛文尼亚在政府支持的议会投票后承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</link><description>上周，斯洛文尼亚政府批准了一项承认巴勒斯坦国的动议，并将其提交议会最终批准。总理加快了这一进程，以回应以色列最近对拉法的袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-04/ty-article/slovenia-recognizes-palestinian-state-after-parliamentary-vote-with-government-support/0000018f-e4de-d11f-a5cf-e7df5fce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>